title: 820-00165 small amount of liquid - now has Magsafe light but no fan.
message:
Hi all.
This board has had a small amount of liquid ingress onto it.

Worst affected areas were around:
U5600-U5601
and, a small amount around:
Q7430-Q7630

I cleaned all areas, and there are no signs of damage.
No feel of any overheating components.

PPDCIN_G3H 15.17V (and with another charger, 16.5v)
PPBUS_G3H 8.6V
PP5V_S5 5.1V
PP3V3_S5 3.3V
PP3V3_SUS 3.3V
PP3V42_G3H 3.44V
PPVRTC_G3H 3.33V

RTC_RESET_L 3.27v
PCH_SRTCRST_L 3.27v
PCH_INTRUDER_L 3.27v
PCH_INTVRMEN 3.27v

Any suggestions?
Thanks for any help you can provide.

title: 820-00165 small amount of liquid - now has Magsafe light but no fan.
message: Trigger SMC_ONOFF_L and check for drop pulse at PM_PWRBTN_L, at same time.

title: 820-00165 small amount of liquid - now has Magsafe light but no fan.
message:
Thanks 2informaticos, and sorry for the delayed reply.
